{"tid":1319206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】圖解黑警包圍合法集會場地 再濫捕和平集會人士","createTime":"2019-07-15T06:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T06:10:36.000Z","uid":74336,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e3067e9e857c32e1d8f33d3dafd685cb74d1681c","tid":1319206,"uid":74336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tY6zVoA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtY6zVoA.png&h=60815e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警夜晚係沙田大會堂拘捕既全部係和平集會人士！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為黑警包圍合法集會場地，然後打算<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1）甕中捉鱉：十一點不反對通知書失效後就將逗留既集會人士以非法集結全數拘捕<br />\n2）抓落單：砌從僅餘逃生路線離開中既集會人士生豬肉，同樣以非法集結拘捕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n發夢夢到琴晚本來沙田百步梯<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">（下圖藍圈）（底下圖藍圈）</span></strong>有合法集會，拎左到不反對通知書到<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十一點</span></strong>。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWfAEQS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeWfAEQS.png&h=421e0e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知到左<strong>九點幾</strong>，黑警從沙田廣場同源禾路方向向沙田百步梯推進，再用盾陣封左<strong>百步梯左側</strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（下圖紅圈）（底下圖紅字1）</strong></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0vwXi9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0vwXi9.png&h=2c7c0bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一時間，黑警從沙田火車站向新城市地下大堂推進，再封鎖左<strong>百步梯往地下大堂兩個出入口</strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（下圖紅圈）（底下圖紅字2）</strong></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSW8e7s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSW8e7s.png&h=12697d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後黑警再封鎖左<strong>通往新城市既天橋</strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（下圖紅圈）（底下圖紅字3）</strong></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mnjats2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnjats2.png&h=882eaee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集會人士得返<strong>百步梯右側</strong>同<strong>百步梯往沙田公園方向</strong>可以走。<br />\n<br />\n但過左冇幾耐，黑警由新城市側門衝出進入合法集會場地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">揮舞警棍恫嚇集會人士</span></span></span>，再封鎖埋<strong>百步梯右側</strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（下圖紅圈）（底下圖紅字4）</span></strong>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c09JOvc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc09JOvc.png&h=d0edf7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集會人士只能從百步梯往沙田公園方向走<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>（底下圖藍字1）</strong></span>，但由於大會堂平台<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（底下圖紅字5）</span></strong>、過河<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（底下圖紅字6）</span></strong>同希爾頓中心方向<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（底下圖紅字7）</span></strong>都有狗，集會人士只能沿河散去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但冇行到呢條路既集會人士最終就比黑警濫捕！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6F4atHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6F4atHg.png&h=a0ec946e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uehSQg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uehSQg.png&h=6b2ed1ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTJ23WQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTJ23WQ.png&h=0300e6b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCredit：東網、立場新聞、ikea窗簾棍"},{"pid":"0b4044a28d474e1b83ae06ddb2c5e9a1ba9729de","tid":1319206,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"341b289765b526608b3bbff68b18d4d88caca606","tid":1319206,"uid":74336,"like":0,"dislike":